Hello <%= @vendor.name %>,

An order has come through on wrapt.com. Please follow this link:

<%= ecommerce_vendor_confirmation_url(@purchase_order.vendor_token) %>

to tell us if you can or cannot fulfill this order. After all other vendors and
purchase orders associated with this customer's entire order are verified, you
will receive the information to complete fulfillment such as shipping labels, a
packling slip, etc.

<% @purchase_order.line_items.each do |line_item| %>
  <% product = line_item.orderable %>
<%= product.vendor_sku %>: <%= product.description %> x <%= line_item.quantity %>
<% end %>

Thanks,
The Wrapt Team
